{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Ja6gQekkSGhNjJe5QYWR54","type":"tool_result","content":"Waiting for server at http://localhost:34338...\nServer is ready!\n\n--- Test: Seeded leagues ---\n  PASS: GET /league/L1 returns 200\n  PASS: L1 name is Mountain\n  PASS: L1 sport is Soccer\n  PASS: GET /league/L2 returns 200\n  PASS: L2 name is Valley\n  PASS: L2 sport is Basketball\n  PASS: GET /league/L3 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /league/L4 returns 200\n  PASS: L4 sport is Snowboarding\n\n--- Test: Create and get league ---\n  PASS: POST /league returns 200\n  PASS: GET /league/L10 returns 200\n  PASS: L10 name is Coast\n  PASS: L10 sport is Baseball\n\n--- Test: Invalid sport ---\n  PASS: POST /league with invalid sport returns 400\n\n--- Test: League not found ---\n  PASS: GET /league/NONEXISTENT returns 404\n\n--- Test: Create team in league ---\n  PASS: POST /team/league/L1 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /team/T100 returns 200\n  PASS: T100 name is Eagles\n  PASS: T100 city is Denver\n  PASS: GET /league/L1/teams returns 200\n  PASS: T100 is in league L1's teams\n\n--- Test: Create player and add to team ---\n  PASS: POST /player returns 200\n  PASS: GET /player/P100 returns 200\n  PASS: P100 name is Test Player\n  PASS: P100 position is forward\n  PASS: P100 salary is 500.0\n  PASS: POST /player/P100/team/T100 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /team/T100/players returns 200\n  PASS: P100 is in team T100\n\n--- Test: Get all players ---\n  PASS: GET /players returns 200\n  PASS: Players list is not empty\n\n--- Test: Player not found ---\n  PASS: GET /player/NONEXISTENT returns 404\n\n--- Test: Players not on team ---\n  PASS: POST create lonely player returns 200\n  PASS: GET /players/not-on-team returns 200\n  PASS: P200 is in not-on-team list\n\n--- Test: Players by position ---\n  PASS: GET /players/position/forward returns 200\n  PASS: At least one forward player found\n  PASS: Player P100 position is forward\n\n--- Test: Players by salary range ---\n  PASS: GET /players/salary/range returns 200\n  PASS: At least one player in salary range\n  PASS: Player P100 salary in range\n\n--- Test: Leagues of player ---\n  PASS: GET /player/P100/leagues returns 200\n  PASS: P100 is in at least one league\n  PASS: P100 is in league L1\n\n--- Test: Sports of player ---\n  PASS: GET /player/P100/sports returns 200\n  PASS: P100 plays at least one sport\n  PASS: P100 plays Soccer\n\n--- Test: Players by league ---\n  PASS: GET /players/league/L1 returns 200\n  PASS: At least one player in league L1\n\n--- Test: Players by sport ---\n  PASS: GET /players/sport/Soccer returns 200\n  PASS: At least one Soccer player\n\n--- Test: Players by city ---\n  PASS: GET /players/city/Denver returns 200\n  PASS: P100 is in Denver\n\n--- Test: Players by higher salary ---\n  PASS: GET /players/salary/higher/LowPay returns 200\n  PASS: At least one player earns more than LowPay\n  PASS: HighPay (P301) earns more than LowPay\n\n--- Test: Drop player from team ---\n  PASS: DELETE /player/P100/team/T100 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /team/T100/players returns 200\n  PASS: P100 is no longer in team T100\n\n--- Test: Remove player ---\n  PASS: DELETE /player/P100 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /player/P100 returns 404 after removal\n\n--- Test: Remove team ---\n  PASS: DELETE /team/T100 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /team/T100 returns 404 after removal\n\n--- Test: Remove league ---\n  PASS: DELETE /league/L10 returns 200\n  PASS: GET /league/L10 returns 404 after removal\n\n============================================================\nResults: 65 passed, 0 failed\n============================================================","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7aa9e9e3-b010-487c-a19d-8b03349f63ee","uuid":"174cca1c-e59b-4234-a1a1-0358cb50c633"}
